snippet.title: NBB.EXE - FINAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
Enter NBB.exe, a very challenging fast-paced precision platformer, inspired by Bomberman and 3D Mario games with a metroidvania twist that invites bombers to explore a mysterious digital world. 

You must jump, dash and bomb your way to triumph in the NBB Arena - to finally uncover the dark secrets that hide in the shadows of NEON industries.

Wishlist the game now at 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2845720/NBBEXE/

And join the community on Discord!
https://discord.gg/payufQ5fwE
